+"""
+MindSense AI — Mental Health Assessment Server  (v4.0)
+======================================================
+Aligned with FINAL FIXED training script (unified_training_final_fixed.py)
+
+Training script produces:
+  Step 1 → rnn_sensor_model.keras   (BiLSTM + GRU + Attention, 6 classes)
+            scaler.pkl
+            label_encoder.pkl
+            state_info.pkl
+
+  Step 2 → facial_cnn_model.keras   (Residual CNN, 7 emotions)
+            facial_cnn_best.keras
+
+  Step 3 → future_predictor_model.keras  (Seq2Seq BiLSTM + Attention)
+            predictor_best.keras
+
+Sensor ranges  : GSR 0–40952  |  PPG 40–200 bpm  |  EEG 0.0–1.0 (normalised)
+Classes (6)    : NORMAL | LOW_STRESS | MODERATE_STRESS | HIGH_ANXIETY | PANIC_STATE | DEPRESSION
+Emotions (7)   : Angry | Disgust | Fear | Happy | Neutral | Sad | Surprise
+
+Run:
+    pip install fastapi uvicorn tensorflow shap opencv-python pillow scikit-learn
+    python deploy_server.py
+"""
